{"tid":2287650,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"SCMP獨家》小蠔灣車廠發展　私樓佔比大減　施政報告公佈詳情","createTime":"2020-11-16T02:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T03:38:11.000Z","uid":35519,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9bf32c48b4a4b801a63bfa9934b9c7b17a3d60","tid":2287650,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/1200x800/public/d8/images/methode/2020/11/16/e4dc03a2-26ee-11eb-8a46-f186a810a22a_image_hires_083227.jpg?itok=eH8z5bUX&amp;v=1605486760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F1200x800%2Fpublic%2Fd8%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2Fe4dc03a2-26ee-11eb-8a46-f186a810a22a_image_hires_083227.jpg%3Fitok%3DeH8z5bUX%26v%3D1605486760&h=0bfa8121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/3109914/lantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhong-kong-economy%2Farticle%2F3109914%2Flantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3gAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a2878011\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/3109914/lantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised</a><br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，原計劃只含私人住宅的小蠔灣車廠項目，在即將發表的施政報告中宣布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n是次將成為港鐵首次參與公營房屋發展，其中多達一半的單位將作為資助房屋出售，其餘的將作為私人房屋出售。<br />\n<br />\n據熟悉此大嶼山項目的消息人士稱，政府已與港鐵商討在大嶼山東北佔地30公頃的小蠔灣車廠的細節。去年，官員們敦促地鐵公司承擔「社會責任」，並在該區提供公營房屋。<br />\n<br />\n過往鐵路營辦商一直透過物業上蓋及週邊地產項目獲取巨額利潤。<br />\n<br />\n根據可行性研究，該區最終落成的單位數量，甚至可能超過最初計劃的14,000個單位。「然而，資助房屋單位亦不太可能佔一半以上。」消息人士亦補充：「公屋與私人住宅並不太兼容。(Public rental flats may not be compatible with private homes)」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aU85qjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaU85qjp.png&h=1ada8553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨海部分將保留給私人市場中的發展商，而靠近高速公路的區域將被用作興建資助房屋，例如居屋和首置計劃申請。<br />\n<br />\n小蠔灣的新地鐵站將成為東涌線的一部分，預計服務人口超過37,000。1995年，政府將香港機場以東5公里的小蠔灣地段劃歸地鐵公司，用於維修保養車廠。如果計劃開發私人住宅和商業項目，鐵路公司將需要支付額外的補地價。<br />\n<br />\n小蠔灣發展原方案：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lXCH0PDzpdjrP39_MoAKRQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9Mjg5/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/hket/HKET_20170717_A02_03_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlXCH0PDzpdjrP39_MoAKRQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9Mjg5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fhket%2FHKET_20170717_A02_03_a.jpg&h=97e83dcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08425e037149a2be78549532aeb3c33054a22117","tid":2287650,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"爽死班蝗蟲 有條大海臏長廊 地鐵站上蓋 有商場 CHILL撚到"},{"pid":"673892c4f623775db4aa30cfdaa5614f05563e53","tid":2287650,"uid":341649,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:39:36.000Z","msg":"Public rental flats may not be compatible with private homes"},{"pid":"752b15fd5e312df01c5db93a4e445e4fe9c6ff4f","tid":2287650,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"唔應該咁做啦"},{"pid":"e388bc005c462dcc82ddd8f25fe0b49f5ecd3c84","tid":2287650,"uid":265485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08425e037149a2be78549532aeb3c33054a22117","tid":2287650,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"爽死班蝗蟲 有條大海臏長廊 地鐵站上蓋 有商場 CHILL撚到"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"起居屋咼，不過冇啦啦係個到起個市鎮勁古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c07faf7f97d412bc5a2dff8faf16ba87a40e6f","tid":2287650,"uid":59494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e388bc005c462dcc82ddd8f25fe0b49f5ecd3c84","tid":2287650,"uid":265485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08425e037149a2b