2Fd8%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2Fe4dc03a2-26ee-11eb-8a46-f186a810a22a_image_hires_083227.jpg%3Fitok%3DeH8z5bUX%26v%3D1605486760&h=0bfa8121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/3109914/lantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhong-kong-economy%2Farticle%2F3109914%2Flantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3gAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a2878011\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/3109914/lantau-seafront-site-yield-thousands-subsidised</a><br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，原計劃只含私人住宅的小蠔灣車廠項目，在即將發表的施政報告中宣布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n是次將成為港鐵首次參與公營房屋發展，其中多達一半的單位將作為資助房屋出售，其餘的將作為私人房屋出售。<br />\n<br />\n據熟悉此大嶼山項目的消息人士稱，政府已與港鐵商討在大嶼山東北佔地30公頃的小蠔灣車廠的細節。去年，官員們敦促地鐵公司承擔「社會責任」，並在該區提供公營房屋。<br />\n<br />\n過往鐵路營辦商一直透過物業上蓋及週邊地產項目獲取巨額利潤。<br />\n<br />\n根據可行性研究，該區最終落成的單位數量，甚至可能超過最初計劃的14,000個單位。「然而，資助房屋單位亦不太可能佔一半以上。」消息人士亦補充：「公屋與私人住宅並不太兼容。(Public rental flats may not be compatible with private homes)」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aU85qjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaU85qjp.png&h=1ada8553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨海部分將保留給私人市場中的發展商，而靠近高速公路的區域將被用作興建資助房屋，例如居屋和首置計劃申請。<br />\n<br />\n小蠔灣的新地鐵站將成為東涌線的一部分，預計服務人口超過37,000。1995年，政府將香港機場以東5公里的小蠔灣地段劃歸地鐵公司，用於維修保養車廠。如果計劃開發私人住宅和商業項目，鐵路公司將需要支付額外的補地價。<br />\n<br />\n小蠔灣發展原方案：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lXCH0PDzpdjrP39_MoAKRQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9Mjg5/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/hket/HKET_20170717_A02_03_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlXCH0PDzpdjrP39_MoAKRQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9Mjg5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fhket%2FHKET_20170717_A02_03_a.jpg&h=97e83dcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"東涌人真係慘<br />\n再起落去第時大嶼山停n個站<br />\n無半個鐘都未去到青衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最早期欣澳同南昌都未有嗰陣<br />\n真係可以半個鐘飛到落香港站"},{"pid":"b6425ddf1676d2a5b7629f2a1e88291643f57740","tid":2287650,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed29d657421ffd6f19e99b9e408e60298facd557","tid":2287650,"uid":288601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e388bc005c462dcc82ddd8f25fe0b49f5ecd3c84","tid":2287650,"uid":265485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08425e037149a2be78549532aeb3c33054a22117","tid":2287650,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"爽死班蝗蟲 有條大海臏長廊 地鐵站上蓋 有商場 CHILL撚到"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"起居屋咼，不過冇啦啦係個到起個市鎮勁古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"似乎政府已經揀定左點都要發展大嶼山<br />\n可能係到時唔知點同明日大嶼相連住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"鐵路：<br />\n屯門南＞掃管笏＞欣澳＞人工島＞堅尼地城<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_B5AFG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_B5AFG_1200x0.png&h=ceab2468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bafced7e7413c634621d117410a9a267d66d75f","tid":2287650,"uid":3063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"咁班私樓人點<br />\n<br />\n月供幾萬供樓<br />\n你鄰居可能係班租都唔洗交<br />\n拎老綜 白卡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家住同一地方 睇同一海景<br />\n（可能佢有海景 你得山景）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5bf958e0ed680de5c7f9f34f9c6add6ca504e0","tid":2287650,"uid":519